<h2>Survey Components</h2>
<p>During the initial licensing period, department zone office staff will conduct an on-site survey to ascertain compliance with the provisions of the Health and Safety Code and associated rules. An entrance conference will be held with key facility personnel. Zone office staff will explain the survey process and answer questions. During the survey, zone office staff will:</p>
<ul>
	<li>Review clinical records</li>
	<li>Review facility policies and procedure</li>
	<li>Review quality assurance activities</li>
	<li>Review personnel records</li>
	<li>Interview staff</li>
	<li>Conduct an exit conference with key facility personnel</li>
	<li>Discuss survey findings</li>
</ul>

